headline: Oppenheimer Reiterates Buy Rating on Ulta Beauty (ULTA) Ahead of Earnings
summary: On May 20, Oppenheimer increased the price target on Ulta Beauty, Inc. (NASDAQ:ULTA) stock from $435 to $465, reiterating a Buy rating on the stock. headline: 2 Unpopular Stocks that Should Get More Attention and 1 to Think Twice About
summary: When Wall Street turns bearish on a stock, it’s worth paying attention. These calls stand out because analysts rarely issue grim ratings on companies for fear their firms will lose out in other business lines such as M&A advisory.
